snippet.title: Longplay of Zaxxon's Motherbase 2000
snippet.description:
Longplay of Zaxxon's Motherbase 2000, played as the NTSC version on the Sega Genesis 32X. This game's version was released in 1995. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

04:01 - Stage 2
08:33 - Stage 3

37:55 - Stage 9
45:08 - Ending + Credits

By: Retro Game Spacko
